Introduction

Minji (민지) is a South Korean singer under O2Clean. She is a former member of the girl group Busters.

On November 18, 2019, Busters announced that Minji had left the group due to personal reasons.

On March 3, 2020, O2Clean announced that she had signed an artist contract with them. Minji released her first solo single "좋아좋아" on November 17, 2021.
